Introduction

Khloe Kim, formerly known as Vita, is a South Korean influencer, and a former rapper, dancer, and singer. She was a member of the girl group MAJORS under ANS Entertainment. After some times of inactivity, her agency announced on May 25, 2022 that Vita hasn't officially left the group but was on an indefinite hiatus due to health/personal reasons. MAJORS ended up disbanding disbanding in 2023. Khloe Kim calls her fans "Klovers", as seen on her SNS bio in which it's written "Welcome KloversüçÄ". She was a contestant on Time Turner.
